input_full.body:
Support two forms for capturing improvement opportunities mid-session:

- `IO` — agent infers the opportunity from surrounding context (zero user tokens)
- `IO(message)` — user provides brief explanation (minimal tokens)

Design rationale: ergonomic keyboard layout (SHIFT + natural finger swipe for parenthesized form), muscle-memory friendly, minimal clock-time cost.
